    "text": "Our 2026 roadmap is here.\n\nQ1: Ship it: French-English live, public API.\nQ2: Prove it: Benchmarks, more languages, institutional partnerships.\nQ3: Refine it: Paraphrasing, context, authenticity.\nQ4: Scale it: Global languages, emotional nuance.\n\nFour quarters. One mission: solve",
