    "text": "Every API key you paste into an AI agent's input box hits their servers in plaintext.\n\nOpenAI keys, Telegram tokens, AWS credentials \u00e2\u0080\u0094 your agent needed them to write a config file, so you just\u00e2\u0080\u00a6 pasted them in. Now they're in the provider's logs, training data, who knows where.",
